WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.310
Hey, good morning family. I have another

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:04.749
video for you all today.

00:00:04.759 --> 00:00:07.110
I've been praying

00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:09.150
early this morning and seeking Him

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:11.190
about what to do for a

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:14.589
video for you all. When I was praying,

00:00:14.599 --> 00:00:16.470
the Lord showed me more about

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:20.029
what's coming.

00:00:20.039 --> 00:00:23.109
I was

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:24.990
going to deliver a lot of this word to

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.189
you and tell you about more preparation,

00:00:28.199 --> 00:00:29.990
but when I was

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.109
at the sink doing the dishes again

00:00:32.119 --> 00:00:34.150
tonight, the Lord spoke to me and He said,

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:37.709
'Brandon, they need a foundation. They're

00:00:37.719 --> 00:00:39.910
going to have to have a foundation of

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:43.389
the Word. You can keep delivering the

00:00:43.399 --> 00:00:45.350
word and telling them what's coming, son,

00:00:45.350 --> 00:00:45.360
but

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:47.350
I'm warning you to pray over this

00:00:47.350 --> 00:00:47.360
stuff.'This

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.229
is what I'm trying to tell you:

00:00:49.239 --> 00:00:51.709
the gross darkness

00:00:51.719 --> 00:00:53.869
that's coming and the things that

00:00:53.879 --> 00:00:56.709
would be like throwing gas

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:58.869
on the fire for you all. I know

00:00:58.879 --> 00:01:01.349
people are curious about what's

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.150
coming, and it's important to know,

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:05.590
but it's more important for you

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:07.310
to have a

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:10.870
foundation of the Word and know how

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:13.550
to stand on it for what's coming

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:16.350
than anything else. You can know

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:18.429
what's coming and be totally destroyed,

00:01:18.439 --> 00:01:20.670
or you can

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:23.149
have a foundation of

00:01:23.159 --> 00:01:25.149
the Word of God and be able to resist,

00:01:25.159 --> 00:01:27.469
stand fast, and know

00:01:27.479 --> 00:01:29.510
how to

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.749
believe for

00:01:31.759 --> 00:01:34.830
things to have victory

00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:36.630
in this

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:39.910
storm. If you don't have the Word and

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:43.030
a concrete foundation—not a

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:47.350
sandy soil

00:01:47.350 --> 00:01:47.360
or

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:49.789
quicksand foundation—we're going to have

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:53.270
a Word-based foundation of solid rock so

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:56.230
that you can build your house on it and the

00:01:56.230 --> 00:01:56.240
storms

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:59.109
of

00:01:59.119 --> 00:02:02.350
life will not blow down your home. But if

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:05.990
you do not have a foundation in the Word

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:08.790
and it's on sand,

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:10.469
your house is going to be swept away

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:12.470
when the wave

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:13.990
comes.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:16.390
We'll get to all that stuff later;

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:18.110
it's not important right now. What's

00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:20.830
important is for you to

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:24.509
understand: have you sat at the feet of

00:02:24.519 --> 00:02:28.350
Jesus today? Have you sat with

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:31.869
Him and started to develop a

00:02:31.879 --> 00:02:34.470
relationship with the Father sitting at

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:36.150
His

00:02:36.160 --> 00:02:39.869
feet? It is so important that you take

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:43.869
the time every day to get in the Word

00:02:43.879 --> 00:02:47.270
and read your

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:51.670
Bible. Find scriptures that pertain to

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:54.550
what you're believing for. Like I've said

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.949
over and over, start

00:02:56.959 --> 00:02:59.589
reading the New Testament all the way

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:00.550
through.

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.949
Read two and

00:03:02.959 --> 00:03:06.270
three chapters a day.

00:03:06.280 --> 00:03:09.270
Spend 20

00:03:09.270 --> 00:03:09.280
to

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:12.550
30 minutes inside the Word. If you can spend 30

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:15.630
minutes on Facebook, Instagram, and

00:03:15.640 --> 00:03:18.750
YouTube watching these videos, you can

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:21.390
take 20 minutes for the Word. I would rather you not

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:24.430
watch any videos at all—mine or

00:03:24.430 --> 00:03:24.440
anyone else's

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:26.589
on the prophetic

00:03:26.589 --> 00:03:26.599
network on YouTube—and

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:28.589
take that time for the Word instead. If you say

00:03:28.589 --> 00:03:28.599
you

00:03:28.599 --> 00:03:30.429
don't have enough time,

00:03:30.439 --> 00:03:32.190
then don't watch my

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:35.309
video; get in the Word. It's more

00:03:35.319 --> 00:03:37.949
important for you to get in the Word

00:03:37.959 --> 00:03:40.830
than to watch me or

00:03:40.840 --> 00:03:43.149
anybody else.

00:03:43.149 --> 00:03:43.159
The

00:03:46.190 --> 00:03:46.200
Word

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:49.990
is

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.550
the

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:56.589
priority in your life, period. Pray. It has

00:03:56.599 --> 00:03:59.789
to be the priority for what's coming,

00:03:59.789 --> 00:03:59.799
or

00:03:59.799 --> 00:04:02.270
you will not make it. I'm just telling

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:05.270
you, that may sound scary, but it needs to

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:08.149
scare you because gross darkness is

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:11.390
coming. Very dark times are coming

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:14.949
for the world, though not for the body of Christ.

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:18.030
Just like it says in Isaiah: 'Arise,

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:20.789
shine, for thy light is come, and the

00:04:20.799 --> 00:04:24.189
glory of the Lord is risen upon

00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:26.670
thee.'The

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:29.350
rest of the verse talks

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:32.230
about great darkness on the earth

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:34.670
because of sin and

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:37.150
gross darkness on the

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:39.590
people.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:42.230
If there's really bad darkness on

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.230
these people and you're the light,

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:45.430
how are you going to

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:47.110
stay

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:50.390
in the light? Have you

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:54.070
sat at the feet of Jesus today? Have you

00:04:54.070 --> 00:04:54.080
listened

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:55.990
to Him and

00:04:55.990 --> 00:04:56.000
talked

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:59.230
to Him about your life,

00:04:59.230 --> 00:04:59.240
your

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:01.150
direction, and where you're supposed to

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:04.670
be living? Are you living in a

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:07.029
high-rise in New York City while

00:05:07.029 --> 00:05:07.039
God is

00:05:07.039 --> 00:05:08.990
trying to tell you to live in

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:11.550
the country? Are you in downtown

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.310
Chicago and God is saying you need to

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:15.550
move? You might have a good job,

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:17.469
but you're not seeking Him

00:05:17.479 --> 00:05:19.070
on another job while He's trying to tell

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:21.950
you to move. I'm telling you, you

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:24.230
need to be in the place that God has for

00:05:24.230 --> 00:05:24.240
you.

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:25.790
Maybe He wants you in those

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:27.390
cities because you're going to be a

00:05:27.400 --> 00:05:29.230
light there, but maybe He's trying to

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.830
tell you to do something else. You

00:05:30.840 --> 00:05:31.950
just need to hear Him. People say

00:05:31.950 --> 00:05:31.960
they

00:05:31.960 --> 00:05:33.950
don't hear His voice at all; it's

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:35.350
because you're not in the Word.

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:37.350
I was listening to

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:39.909
statistics from Pastor

00:05:39.919 --> 00:05:43.230
Steve, who said

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:46.710
97% of all Christians don't read their

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:51.510
Bible on a daily basis and only 3%

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:53.670
have read the Word all the

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:54.469
way

00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:56.590
through. When I heard that

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:59.189
statistic at church, I thought, 'This is

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:00.790
serious.'The

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:03.189
foundation of the Word is what's

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:05.830
going to get you through hard times. You

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:08.790
have got to get that Bible out and read

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:10.430
it. If you say

00:06:10.440 --> 00:06:11.870
it's too hard to

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:15.150
understand, get a translation that you

00:06:15.150 --> 00:06:15.160
do

00:06:15.160 --> 00:06:18.230
understand. It may be

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:20.469
the New Living Translation—there

00:06:20.469 --> 00:06:20.479
are

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:22.309
all kinds of really good translations.

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:36.430
Let's not

00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:42.029
get religious about this. If you don't understand the King James Version, find a

00:06:42.039 --> 00:06:45.070
Bible that ministers to you. If

00:06:45.070 --> 00:06:45.080
you're

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:46.390
a teenager and

00:06:46.390 --> 00:06:46.400
you

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:48.749
can only understand

00:06:48.749 --> 00:06:48.759
something

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:51.189
like

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:54.110
The Message Bible,

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:56.270
that's

00:06:56.280 --> 00:06:58.670
better than nothing. Read

00:06:58.670 --> 00:06:58.680
the

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:01.110
Word.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:03.350
It may be modernized,

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:20.070
but it's the

00:07:20.070 --> 00:07:20.080
Word

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:21.670
of

00:07:21.670 --> 00:07:21.680
God

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:23.350
and it's going to

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:27.309
change your life.

00:07:27.319 --> 00:07:29.550
The

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:32.189
Amplified Bible is also a good

00:07:32.199 --> 00:07:34.710
version that will

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:36.869
help you.

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:49.230
I read all kinds

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:50.830
of different translations because

00:07:50.840 --> 00:07:52.830
everything ministers to me differently.

00:07:56.520 --> 00:07:57.869
Let's just get in the Word and

00:07:57.869 --> 00:07:57.879
not

00:07:57.879 --> 00:08:01.670
be petty.

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:04.629
Read two or three chapters

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:07.110
every day.

00:08:12.039 --> 00:08:15.189
When I

00:08:15.189 --> 00:08:15.199
talk

00:08:15.199 --> 00:08:17.230
about practicing the presence of

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:21.589
the Lord, I'm talking about

00:08:23.319 --> 00:08:25.110
visualizing

00:08:27.039 --> 00:08:30.710
Him being there with you. Talk to Him like you'd

00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:30.720
talk to your son or daughter.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:34.509
Visualize that Jesus Christ is

00:08:34.519 --> 00:08:36.909
living on the inside of

00:08:36.909 --> 00:08:36.919
you.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:39.630
I'm not saying to pretend;

00:08:41.680 --> 00:08:45.190
Jesus is real

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:48.389
and He is living on the inside of you.

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:50.910
You practice His presence by

00:08:50.910 --> 00:08:50.920
thinking,

00:08:50.920 --> 00:08:54.310
'Jesus, how is Your day

00:08:54.310 --> 00:08:54.320
today?'Visualize

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:57.829
Him

00:08:57.839 --> 00:09:00.069
sitting there with

00:09:02.079 --> 00:09:03.710
you. Think about

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:06.150
it in your head: Jesus is in me, He is with me, and I'm

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:08.350
going to practice talking to Him. Don't

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:10.269
act like He's far

00:09:10.269 --> 00:09:10.279
away.

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:12.590
He said, 'I'll never leave you

00:09:12.590 --> 00:09:12.600
nor

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:14.389
forsake you; lo, I am with you always, even unto the

00:09:14.399 --> 00:09:17.110
end of the

00:09:17.110 --> 00:09:17.120
world.'That

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:19.150
means He is dwelling in you.

00:09:19.150 --> 00:09:19.160
The

00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:21.910
very

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:23.990
atmosphere can get charged with the

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:26.030
power of the Holy Ghost if you start

00:09:26.040 --> 00:09:28.069
worshiping and

00:09:28.079 --> 00:09:30.509
meditating on His Word.

00:09:30.519 --> 00:09:34.630
Lord, I

00:09:34.640 --> 00:09:37.790
want to know You more; teach me Your ways.

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:43.150
The Bible says His sheep will

00:09:43.160 --> 00:09:45.750
know His voice, and a stranger's voice they

00:09:45.750 --> 00:09:45.760
will

00:09:45.760 --> 00:09:47.470
not

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:49.710
follow. How do you

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:53.269
know someone's voice?

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:59.750
You become

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:02.470
familiar with them. If my wife calls me,

00:10:09.399 --> 00:10:12.550
I

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:18.230
know her voice immediately. If my son

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:20.310
calls, I

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.269
know immediately

00:10:22.269 --> 00:10:22.279
it's

00:10:22.279 --> 00:10:24.470
him.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:27.269
Why?

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:30.230
Because you've spent time with them

00:10:30.230 --> 00:10:30.240
and

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:32.630
developed a relationship

00:10:32.640 --> 00:10:36.389
over years.

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:43.629
It's

00:10:46.079 --> 00:10:49.110
the same way

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:51.350
you develop a relationship with the Lord;

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:53.509
you spend time with Him. The more time

00:10:53.519 --> 00:10:56.230
you spend in prayer

00:10:56.230 --> 00:10:56.240
and

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:59.310
reading His Word,

00:10:59.320 --> 00:11:01.790
the more you're going to know His voice.

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:16.670
For instance, my

00:11:16.680 --> 00:11:19.509
grandfather was one of my best friends.

00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:28.430
I knew his voice

00:11:28.430 --> 00:11:28.440
perfectly,

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:31.430
but he passed

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:34.269
away 12 years

00:11:34.279 --> 00:11:37.550
ago. I began to forget how his voice

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:40.509
sounded until I found an old video recording of

00:11:40.509 --> 00:11:40.519
him.

00:11:40.519 --> 00:11:42.829
I heard his voice and started

00:11:42.839 --> 00:11:45.790
crying because it was so precious

00:11:45.800 --> 00:11:47.790
to me.

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:03.350
Once you go back to it, you

00:12:03.350 --> 00:12:03.360
don't

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:05.230
forget it again. But if you don't

00:12:05.240 --> 00:12:08.069
spend quality time with that

00:12:08.079 --> 00:12:10.629
voice, you start to

00:12:10.639 --> 00:12:12.629
forget the

00:12:12.629 --> 00:12:12.639
pitch.

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:15.269
You've

00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:30.710
got

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:46.990
to read

00:12:46.990 --> 00:12:47.000
the

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:50.030
Bible

00:12:50.040 --> 00:12:50.949
and

00:12:50.959 --> 00:12:53.230
pray.

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:55.470
Let's

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:57.470
make a plan

00:12:57.470 --> 00:12:57.480
to

00:12:57.480 --> 00:12:59.750
get in

00:12:59.750 --> 00:12:59.760
the

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:02.389
Word every

00:13:02.389 --> 00:13:02.399
day.

00:13:02.399 --> 00:13:04.389
We can start it now

00:13:04.389 --> 00:13:04.399
for

00:13:04.399 --> 00:13:07.470
the Jewish New Year; let's do it in Rosh

00:13:07.470 --> 00:13:07.480
Hashanah.

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:09.710
We don't have

00:13:09.710 --> 00:13:09.720
to wait for

00:13:09.720 --> 00:13:11.110
January. If you

00:13:13.800 --> 00:13:18.590
feed

00:13:22.040 --> 00:13:25.150
your flesh

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:30.350
three times a day,

00:13:33.230 --> 00:13:33.240
but

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:38.790
your spirit is starving, you're

00:13:38.790 --> 00:13:38.800
in trouble.

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:41.710
Most people only feed their spirit for 30 minutes on

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:44.310
Sunday.

00:13:49.720 --> 00:13:51.670
If you go to a

00:13:51.680 --> 00:13:53.990
mega church

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:55.590
and

00:13:55.600 --> 00:13:57.269
the

00:13:57.279 --> 00:13:59.389
only Bible time you have is reading scriptures on

00:13:59.399 --> 00:14:01.310
the teleprompter, that's

00:14:01.320 --> 00:14:02.749
not

00:14:02.759 --> 00:14:05.629
enough.

00:14:05.639 --> 00:14:09.069
Your spirit needs to eat

00:14:09.079 --> 00:14:12.670
in the morning and at night. If

00:14:12.680 --> 00:14:15.069
you start feeding your spirit, your

00:14:15.069 --> 00:14:15.079
life is

00:14:15.079 --> 00:14:17.790
going

00:14:17.800 --> 00:14:20.030
to change

00:14:20.040 --> 00:14:21.829
because

00:14:21.839 --> 00:14:26.790
God is the Word.

00:14:30.399 --> 00:14:34.030
He inspired

00:14:34.040 --> 00:14:36.230
those words; they are Him, and they

00:14:36.230 --> 00:14:36.240
bring

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:38.030
life into

00:14:40.040 --> 00:14:42.150
you.

00:14:43.759 --> 00:14:46.189
It's like taking a

00:14:46.199 --> 00:14:49.150
