00:39:13.760 --> 00:39:16.589
We rejoiced

00:39:16.589 --> 00:39:16.599
because

00:39:16.599 --> 00:39:18.190
we got to

00:39:18.200 --> 00:39:22.550
eat!

00:39:22.560 --> 00:39:25.710
God comes through.

00:39:25.720 --> 00:39:27.870
He's

00:39:27.880 --> 00:39:30.710
been faithful to me when

00:39:30.710 --> 00:39:30.720
I've

00:39:30.720 --> 00:39:33.109
had nothing.

00:39:37.319 --> 00:39:40.430
Don't give up.

00:39:40.440 --> 00:39:42.990
You've got to learn

00:39:43.000 --> 00:39:45.670
how to believe by faith.

00:39:48.880 --> 00:39:51.349
God's going to do

00:39:51.359 --> 00:39:54.069
an accelerated time for

00:39:54.079 --> 00:39:57.109
you

00:40:02.000 --> 00:40:04.550
because Jesus

00:40:04.560 --> 00:40:09.030
is coming. I bless you all in the

00:40:09.040 --> 00:40:11.550
mighty name of Jesus. I believe for

00:40:11.560 --> 00:40:14.230
healing and prosperity for you.

00:40:24.480 --> 00:40:28.390
Put a smile on your face

00:40:28.400 --> 00:40:31.550
and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you,

00:40:31.560 --> 00:40:34.910
and we love you. We will see

00:40:34.920 --> 00:40:37.990
you next time. Have a blessed and

00:40:38.000 --> 00:40:42.079
wonderful day. Bye-bye.

